<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.6.4">
<l>mallai munnī ratarpaṭava riveñ cilaikāl vaḷaivittu</l>
<l>kollai vilaṅku paṇiceyyak koṭiyō ṉilaṅkai pukaluṟṟu</l>
<l>tollai maraṅkaḷ pukappeytu tuvalai nimirntu vāṉaṇava</l>
<l>kallāl kaṭalai yaṭaittāṉūr kaṇṇa puramnām toḻutumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We will worship in Kaṇṇapuram, the city of the one</l>
<l rend="indent">who blocked the sea with stones,</l>
<l>When forest creatures performed the work, so that a pathway arose</l>
<l rend="indent">in the great three-watered [sea],</l>
<l>As ancient trees went into [the water], so spraying droplets rose up</l>
<l rend="indent">and reached the heaven,</l>
<l>Having made the tips of the striped, fierce bow bend, intending entry</l>
<l rend="indent">into the cruel one’s Laṅkā.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
